title: G-SHOCK Camouflage featuring GDX6900CM Watch Collection
description: G-SHOCK unveils a new collection of entirely modern watches with an all-over coating of a classic tiger and woodland camouflage prints that match the rough-and-ready nature of the watches. The camo series by G-SHOCK will be released in two waves this spring. The first watch to hit the streets is the XL GDX6900CM, with multi-angle tiger camo printed case, band and dial, available in two colorways: tan and grey. With an emphasis on superior performance and unrivaled functionality. The second release, GD120CM is a new formidable case design with a 7-year battery that dons a woodland camouflage multi-angle print. Its large case size (51.2mm) has all the same functionality as the GDX6900CM, and is available in three bold colorways: red, tan and grey.
